          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1648543093821-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain and shake the <strong>potatoes</strong> around the colander to fluff up the edges, then chop your <strong>broccoli</strong> into small florets and cut the<strong> stem[s]</strong> into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong>, then peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Top, tail and slice your <strong>carrot[s]</strong> at an angle, then reboil a kettle</p><p>Add your <strong>rump steak[s]</strong> to a bowl with <strong>half </strong>your <strong>Henderson's Relish </strong>(save the rest for later!) and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>and<strong> </strong>set aside</p>",
