    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the<strong> steak[s]</strong> is done, transfer to a clean board to rest, reserving the pan</p><p>Return the reserved pan to a medium heat with a knob of <strong>butter </strong>and 2 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tsp]</span> <strong>flour</strong> and cook for 30 secs</p><p>Whisk in the<strong> beef & onion stock</strong>, then bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 4-5 min or until thickened – this is your <strong>beef & onion gravy</strong></p>",
